#  To-Do List Website

This is a simple web application that helps users manage their daily tasks.

##  Features
- Add new tasks
- View a list of tasks
- Mark tasks as completed using a checklist
- Delete tasks
- Automatically stores tasks so they remain available after refreshing the page

##  Technologies Used
- HTML
- CSS
- JavaScript

##  Project Structure
index.html
style.css
script.js

##  How to Use
1. Enter a task in the input field
2. Click the **Add** button to add the task
3. Click on a task to mark it as completed
4. Remove tasks when they are no longer needed
5. Tasks are saved automatically

##  Purpose
This project was created to practice basic web development concepts such as DOM manipulation, event handling, and local storage.

